109
00:06:55,528 --> 00:06:57,528
Sangat benar.

110
00:06:57,528 --> 00:07:00,828
Maksudmu mereka jatuh cinta selama itu?

111
00:07:01,728 --> 00:07:02,728
Hei...

112
00:07:02,728 --> 00:07:04,228
Ya!

113
00:07:04,228 --> 00:07:07,528
