142
00:08:39,328 --> 00:08:42,528
Tapi mantelnya berada di kursi.

143
00:08:42,528 --> 00:08:45,028
Kenapa pembunuhnya repot-repot menutupi jasad dengan taplak meja?

144
00:08:45,028 --> 00:08:47,028
Alasannya adalah...

145
00:08:47,028 --> 00:08:52,128
taplak meja abu-abu itu tampak lebih hangat daripada mantel hitam itu.

146
00:08:52,128 --> 00:08:53,128
Hah?

147
00:08:53,128 --> 00:08:57,328
Hei, jangan bilang bahwa kau serius dengan apa yang kau katakan barusan.

148
00:08:58,428 --> 00:08:59,628
Ya ampun.

149
00:08:59,628 --> 00:09:02,928
Kau memberikan petunjuk di prolog pembuka.

150
00:09:02,928 --> 00:09:06,928
Kenapa abu-abu tampak lebih hangat daripada hitam?

151
00:09:06,928 --> 00:09:09,228
Apa? Bukankah begitu menurutmu?

152
00:09:10,928 --> 00:09:13,728
Temanmu tidak begitu hebat, ya?

153
00:09:13,728 --> 00:09:16,428
Ayah, bicara yang serius.

154
00:09:16,428 --> 00:09:19,528
Ayo. Seriuslah, Kogoro!

155
00:09:19,528 --> 00:09:23,028
Tidak mungkin! Sampai sini sahaja pria tua ini.

156
00:09:28,528 --> 00:09:30,028
Ya ampun.

157
00:09:30,028 --> 00:09:31,628
Dia sudah muncul!

158
00:09:31,628 --> 00:09:33,828
Kogoro Tidur!

159
00:09:33,828 --> 00:09:35,728
Permisi.

160
00:09:35,728 --> 00:09:37,928
Karena deduksinya sangat sederhana,

161
00:09:37,928 --> 00:09:39,528
