208
00:12:04,428 --> 00:12:06,328
Dasar...

209
00:12:06,328 --> 00:12:08,928
Aku akan tidur di ruangan di belakang hingga aku merasa lebih semangat,

210
00:12:08,928 --> 00:12:11,328
